{"tid":2495533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵施暴壓頸 乘客神經受損雙手癱瘓 經查屬合資格","createTime":"2021-04-19T08:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:51:23.000Z","uid":354250,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"016c209027bdf0c4db327da52566274f3a078064","tid":2495533,"uid":354250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=5cbf758e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU%2F&h=800c9083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n一名為精神病殘疾的青年持特惠票出閘，5名職員立即截查，疑惹起對方不滿，結果演變成「5對1」、有如執法人員制服市民的戲碼<br />\n<br />\n據悉，青年持有殘疾證明，事發時使用殘疾人士八達通出閘，亦有公立醫院精神科醫療紀錄文件證明，早前曾被港鐵職員兩度查證。<br />\n<br />\n涉事姓林（21歲）青年仍然在東區醫院留醫，其頸部劇痛，疑神經線受損，手部麻痺及刺痛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcJK5WQsUtjPUnozJd8cXJ3AUQMErW3Dfhh2pNLnRJd3u?filename=u9dfB6S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9dfB6S.png&h=49fb17c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，今日收到消息指，根據港鐵今日內部流傳，港鐵顧客服務及收益保護組要求相關同事統一口供，指出係當時紅衫職員不斷挑撥以及不斷教唆該青年乘客唔好合作，導致職員需要行駛合適武力拘留乘客。並且盡量focus自己才是受害人的要點，以及produce較多財物被損壞以及自己的傷勢等等證據，及要求各人見醫生，以自己方法盡量展示更多傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n內容提到，由於紅衫乘客並非職員，無權插手乘客查票事宜，可以將青年神經損害責任歸咎去呢位乘客，指出因為有乘客加入圍捕行動，導致事件急遽升溫惡化，責任完全不在公司。<br />\n<br />\n裏面亦提到，相關職員持有保安牌照，公司對跪頸制服激動乘客予以認同，又表示相關同事可以自衛為理由作出抗辯，認為即使對乘客造成嚴重損害，都只是盡責地「immobilize」乘客。<br />\n<br />\n有關紅衫乘客照片已經內部傳閱，並且紅圈圈起，內部又表示日內會發函支持有關職員，以及拒絕承認責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZESn5oR48yEbjLGohKa5DwRUPnLYu4jxxqVjagMSEFgo?filename=jKZyoKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjKZyoKj.jpg&h=3f336f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他報導圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcVX4mRPA8C8eWqHv1DNwSy6RCK8vCjJTrQ4HXiPe3raf?filename=dTUKvkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTUKvkD.jpg&h=d0fb7c0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f58310906b0465d3211c5e8d71a0ea006a65341","tid":2495533,"uid":5737,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"合資格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議當事人告鳩佢地啦<br />\n歧視殘疾人士加暴力對待"},{"pid":"deee81f445435729eec97f49fc355312328a39ec","tid":2495533,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合資格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議當事人告鳩佢地啦<br />\n歧視殘疾人士加暴力對待</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為佢話合資格用暴力"},{"pid":"f0f23add158a4e8ebc0bc1ec1abd6521479ec532","tid":2495533,"uid":121937,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"睇圖仲以為紅衫落手一齊制服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e0608474111e7b9d75bc7734ee09df9d69a916","tid":2495533,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"george floyd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a06d2a5e8a32524c49ede38c96005288eaa993","tid":2495533,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"紅衫好心就推開黃衫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 